trans-unit.source: Adds a custom stream upgrade provider to a custom binding.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en egendefinert dataflyten oppgradering leverandør en egendefinert binding.

trans-unit.source: To indicate that a custom stream upgrade provider should be used, implement a binding element that implements this `abstract` class on the custom binding.
trans-unit.target: For å angi en egendefinert dataflyten oppgradering leverandør som skal brukes, implementere et bindingselement som implementerer dette `abstract` klasse for den egendefinerte bindingen.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeBindingElement"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeBindingElement"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeBindingElement"></xref> class from an existing instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeBindingElement"> </xref> klassen fra en eksisterende forekomst.

trans-unit.source: The instance of this class to be cloned.
Creates an instance on the client of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider"></xref> based on the channel context provided.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst på klienten for den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider"> </xref> basert på kanal kontekst som er angitt.

trans-unit.source: This method is called when opening the client channel factory and provides a custom implementation of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>`abstract` class.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles når du åpner klienten kanalfabrikken og gir en egendefinert implementering av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider> `abstract` klasse.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext> parameter enables reacting to other elements in the channel stack.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>parameteren aktiverer reagere til andre elementer i kanal-stakken.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext> for the entire channel stack.
Creates an instance on the server of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider"></xref> based on the channel context provided.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en forekomst på serveren for den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider"> </xref> basert på kanal kontekst som er angitt.

trans-unit.source: This method is called when opening the service and provides a custom implementation of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>`abstract` class.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles når du åpner tjenesten og gir en egendefinert implementering av <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider> `abstract` klasse.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.StreamUpgradeProvider>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext> parameter enables reacting to other elements in the channel stack.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>parameteren aktiverer reagere til andre elementer i kanal-stakken.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.BindingContext> for the entire channel stack.
